Introduction

Kim Youngkyun, also known by his stage name Hwiyoung, is a South Korean singer, rapper, songwriter, and actor under FNC Entertainment. He debuted as a member of SF9 on October 5, 2016, with the group's first single album "Feeling Sensation".

He made his solo debut with the digital single "Drive5" on August 13, 2023.

In 2018, he participated as a contestant in Mnet's "High School Rapper 2".
